description:
Supermodel Linda Evangelista talks "Gianni" (Versace), "Georgie" (Michael), and beauty tips she's learned during her legendary career. Before that, we share highlights from New York Fashion Week, discuss adventures in facial-ing, and obsess about gummy hair vitamins.
